These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Birthday   | april | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter |

 #################################

 
